			<br>&nbsp;<u><i><font color="#FFFF00">BASIC CONTROLS:</font></i></u><br>
                  &nbsp; Move character:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;D-Pad or Left Analog Stick</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Cancel action:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;X Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Spirit Explosion (Life Bar Decreases, OSP Gauge and GP Increased):
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;X Button + D-Pad or Left Analog Stick Forward</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Deflect:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;X Button + D-Pad or Left Analog Stick Backward</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Select action / Strong attack:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Circle Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Special Move:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Square Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Weak attack:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Triangle Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Backward Dash (Step Out):
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;L1 Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Dash (Step In):
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;R1 Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Pause game:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Start Button</font><br>
			<br>&nbsp;<u><i><font color="#FFFF00">OBSTACLE RACE MINI GAME CONTROLS:</font></i></u><br>
                  &nbsp; Jump:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;X Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Run:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp; Square & Circle Buttons</font><br><br>
